Description: Qt6 GUI for memtester with iOS-style design
 Memtester GUI is a Qt6-based graphical interface for the memtester
 memory testing tool. It provides an iOS-inspired design with
 card-based layout, real-time test progress, and comprehensive
 memory testing options.
 .
 Features:
  - Chinese interface with all CLI functionality
  - Real-time test progress and results display
  - Memory size and loop count configuration
  - Advanced options (physical address mapping, unlocked memory)
  - Test selection with 15 memory test types
